Plate <- 
Plate %>% 
  pivot_longer(-row, names_to = "col", values_to = "Sample") %>% 
  mutate(Well = paste(row, col, sep = "")) %>% 
  dplyr::select(Sample, Well) %>% 
  filter(!is.na(Sample))
Meta <- 
  Plate %>% 
  select(Sample) %>% 
  mutate(Name = gsub("(.+?)_.+", "\\1", Sample),
         Dillution = as.numeric(gsub(".+?_(.+)", "\\1", Sample)),
         Type = case_when(grepl("POS", Sample) ~ "Pos_control",
                          grepl("BLANK", Sample) ~ "Extr_blank",
                          grepl("PCR", Sample) ~ "PCR_neg",
                          TRUE ~ "Sample"))

PCR_fit <- 
HB %>% 
  group_by(Sample) %>% 
  nest() %>% 
  mutate(pcrfit = map(data, ~pcrfit(cyc = 1, fluo = 3, data = .))) %>% 
  mutate(CT = map(pcrfit, ~predict(.x, 
                                   newdata = tibble(Fluo = c(20)),
                                   which = "x",
                                   interval = c("prediction"),
                                   level = 0.95)))

 # mutate(CT = c(10)) %>%
  left_join(Meta) %>%

  mutate(CT_diff_exp = rep(c(1, log(5/2,2), 1), 17)) %>%
